parameters:
Thief Nora: A strong scent of blood... Could this possibly
be...!?

Priestess Sophia: They're already dead. Their throat has
been slit with a sharp blade.
Clea: It seems like we should inform Cors-san about this.

Organization's Patrol Squad: You guys! What are you doing in
our territory!

Organization's Patrol Squad: A male corpse... I see... I
didn't expect there to be multiple people.
Thief Nora: W-Wait, it's just a misunderstanding, okay!?

Organization's Patrol Squad: For the sake of our boss...
We'll defeat you and your Derringer!
Clea: We defeated them in the heat of the moment, didn't we?

Thief Nora: It's bad if the misunderstanding isn't cleared
up!

Cors the Wanderer: Ahaha, you guys always find yourselves in
troublesome situations whenever it gets noisy, huh?

Cors the Wanderer: There are some things that I can't let
them hear. If you're okay with it, shall we have a chat
while looking at the sea?

Cors the Wanderer: Encountering someone with extraordinary
knife skills like Delia's short sword is quite unfortunate,
isn't it?

Captain Clevo: You're the man searching for the beastmen...
I'll make sure you spill the name of the noble who hired
you.

Cors the Wanderer: I apologize for the inconvenience, but
could you provide me with some support?

Captain Clevo: Help me, Nora. You should be able to find out
the whereabouts of the noble from this person.

Thief Nora: You've got it all wrong! Both of you, put away
your weapons, please!
Thief Nora: First, we need to talk it out!

Cors the Wanderer: Oh my, what a disgrace. I didn't even
notice you tailing me. My apologies for the inconvenience.
Captain Clevo: So, have you found out anything?

Clea: I asked someone with connections to the nobility, and
they said that many of the people who were killed were fond
of womanizing.
Clea: Could the culprit be disguised as a prostitute?

Cors the Wanderer: If that's the case, it makes sense that
the men who were killed didn't show any signs of resistance,
huh?
Captain Clevo: I'll disguise myself and lure them out.

Cors the Wanderer: I will take you to places where it is
likely that the noble people will encounter prostitutes.

Cors the Wanderer: These are the nobles who owe me a big
debt, hehehe. In times like these, it's all about give and
take, you know.

Cors the Wanderer: The Delye Dagger is capable of committing
widespread murder. This is the perfect opportunity to
showcase the power of our organization.

Cors the Wanderer: Leave the fighting to all of you and rest
comfortably in the office until then, please.
